# 🧠 FPGA-Based Olfactory Detection System (PCA + Classifier)

## 📌 Overview
This project implements a **hardware-based olfactory detection system** using FPGA. The system processes multi-sensor inputs, applies **Principal Component Analysis (PCA)** for feature extraction, and performs **risk classification** in real time.

The design is developed using **Verilog HDL**, simulated in ModelSim, and synthesized using Quartus Prime.

